      <talk_answer link_index="n1807_desert_velskud-3-" mid="138" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="137"><![CDATA[<html>$Velskud$<BR>…………….</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1807_desert_velskud-4" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Velskud_Human.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1807_desert_velskud-4-a" mid="109" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="37"><![CDATA[<html>$Velskud$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Velskud looks pale.)</FONT> I guess this would calm down Argenta's jewel a little...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1807_desert_velskud-4-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Velskud_Human.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1807_desert_velskud-4-b" mid="110" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="38"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Are you all right, Velskud? Please don't push yourself too hard.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1807_desert_velskud-4-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Velskud_Human.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1807_desert_velskud-4-c" mid="111" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="39"><![CDATA[<html>$Velskud$<BR>It's just that I’m still not used to this power. Don't make such a fuss. Besides, the <FONT color=#a82424>two women</FONT> keep whispering to me in my sleep like they've left their souls in the jewels and it's giving me insomnia.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1807_desert_velskud-4-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Velskud_Human.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1807_desert_velskud-4-d" mid="112" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="40"><![CDATA[<html>$Velskud$<BR>I can't stand those fools… They are so scared that the world they've been protecting might be destroyed… How ridiculous...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1807_desert_velskud-4-d" image="QN_Npc_Argenta.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Velskud_Human.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1807_desert_velskud-4-e" mid="113" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="41"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>(Is it because of the jewel? I somehow feel like talking to Argenta when I talk to Velskud now...)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1807_desert_velskud-4-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Velskud_Human.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1807_desert_velskud-4-f" mid="114" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="42"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Well, we have one less thing to worry about now. Everything would be great if Rubinart and Geraint are back safely…</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1807_desert_velskud-4-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Velskud_Human.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1807_desert_velskud-4-g" mid="115" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="43"><![CDATA[<html>$Velskud$<BR>You don't have to worry about Rubinart since his barrier is still up. You don't have to worry about the noisy kid too. Though it's vague, I can still feel that he's somewhere in Mistland.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1807_desert_velskud-4-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Velskud_Human.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1807_desert_velskud-4-h" mid="116" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="44"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Really? That's a relief... It would be good if you can help me find Geraint too… But I guess the poison in Mistland would be too much for you to bear...</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
